title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4' game
maintext:
BATON ROUGE, La. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Louisiana Lottery’s “Pick 4” game were:
6-9-7-2
(six, nine, seven, two)
